dc_title_s: Bus Routes City of Madison, Wisconsin, 2016
dc_description_s: This line data layer represents bus routes for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Madison_City_BusRoutes_2016.gdb. Other feature classes in this geodatabase include: Bus_Stops, ParkRide, Route_Pattern, Route_Trips, Suburban_Transit_Routes and Suburban_Transit_Stops.
dc_creator_sm: City of Madison - Metropolitan Planning Organization (MPO)
